lead_paragraph: James Magnussen is still driven by the memory of his heartbreaking loss in the 100 metres freestyle final at the London Olympics and the Australian cannot wait to "set things straight" in Rio later this year.

headline.print_headline: Australia's Magnussen Has Unfinished Olympic Business
